Aprils was the reason why I got heavily into this newfound passion for fishkeeping as the young fry I was to the hobby and will always be the main part of my aquatics journey. I met the store owner, Darrin Stewart, at the shop who always engages with each and every person stopping in and I recently found out that he is always the one personally delivering my orders. This speaks a lot about how important it is to them that everyone who shops with April s is always extremely satisfied with their products and service. Thank you for taking such good care of me over the years. See you again real soon!
response_from_owner_text: Ohh my goodness, it sounds as if we paid you to say all these lovely things about us Yooks. We do try our level best and this kind of recognition and support is exactly what the doctor ordered and is more appreciated than you would think. Overall business in any shape or form is finding it tough these days more in particular retail and the bare facts are simple, you support us , we support you , and if things are not 100% we will do everything in our control to put right and more. All the thanks and appreciation is to our customers for their unwavering support and we will take good care of you for many years to come that is our promise. Thanks again for everything and of course we hope to see you very soon @yourlocalfishstore

review_text: I highly reccommend Aprils Aquariums, they went above & beyond to make my order possible. I have been waiting a long time for access to Aquarium Co-ops products so needless to say Im thrilled. My order arrived today & I was thrilled, the plant I ordered arrived in good condition. I hope everyone will give them a try, you wont be disappointed & the owner Darren is awesome.I will be ordering again in a couple of months.
response_from_owner_text: Cheryl - I usually provide a detailed personal response from the heart - but with this absolutely perfect review of our services - I have only one sentence for you - You are awesome .

review_text: Great conversation with owner, super clean and healthy tanks, nice diversity of fish. I appreciate that I went to get my hands on some ACO gear (without paying shipping to my Ontario home), and the staff were willing to help me without making a big sale. As a result, they ll keep my business in the future, via mail.
response_from_owner_text: Thank you for your fantastic candid and honest review. Thanks for coming by and it was indeed a pleasure to meet you . We would be more then happy to ship you  our offerings across to ON and look forward to hearing from you when your ready. Thanks for all your support Cheers

review_text: My partner and I went to Aprils Aquarium as newcomers to aquascaping and were blown away by the friendliness and knowledge of Darrin and his staff at the Marine Drive location. They approached us with such intrigue to our projects and considered our budget and gave us realistic advice for which plants would work in our tanks with our fish. I got a piece of beautiful wood and lots of plants and we ended up going back for more things such as fluval stratum substrate, a filter, moss and more. The plants were in great health, and have taken well in our tanks. The store is clean and much bigger than I expected, it was a blast exploring around and looking at all the tanks of different species id never seen before. Definitely recommend Aprils Aquariums for advanced to even beginner aquascapers!
response_from_owner_text: Emily - what a fantastic review , thank you so much . We also really do appreciate your valuable business and thank you so much for this also . Please tell all your friends and family and of course we hope to see you both again very soon . Cheers to you .

review_text: Aprils takes better care of their fish than any other store Ive been to! I never lose a single one when they arrive. Their stocking is great, and the Aquarium Co-Op products are fantastic to have access to!
response_from_owner_text: Serena, What a fantastic review, thank you ! We pride ourselves in a process that we do not sell livestock that is not healthy and we feel has longevity. We quarantine all new livestock for a minimum 7 days. This is our success for sure as we simply do not want unhappy customers and with all due respect the fish are more important to us, if they are good our customers are good, thus everyone is happy. We truly appreciate you recognizing this, as many stores do not follow our positive practises and processes.  Why ? because it costs money. Thank you for all your valuable business and support and of course we hope to hear from you again very soon @yourlocalfishstore

review_text: Love love this store!! Been awesome all around, great service and all products plants, livestock have been perfect. So nice to have such a great service in Canada. Aquarium co-op is a totally perfect touch I trust Cory threw and threw and the folks at Aprils Aquarium!! Thank you all for what you do!!!!
response_from_owner_text: Wes , what a beauty of a review sir. We cannot thank-you enough for all your support and long May that continue. We are delighted your happy with our offerings and service and of course we hope to hear from you soon @yourlocalfishstore

review_text: It is my first time to order fish from this store online. I had the fish delivered to east coast yesterday. They are healthy and doing well with my other corycats. It is a pleasure to talk Darrin over the phone. I will visit  the store while I am vacation in Vancouver
response_from_owner_text: Benjamin, I was indeed a pleasure helping you out with your livestock. Yes 4,000 miles is a long way and we are delighted our process of packing and heat-packs made for a successful transaction, but more importantly the fish arrived healthy and strong. We appreciate all the support, your business your fantastic review and your commitments to our great hobby in general. We hope to hear from you again very soon @yourlocalfishstore

review_text: First time ordering my supplies on line. Everything arrived well packaged and in good condition. I used to go to the store in Bby, which was always a great experience, but with that stores closure the travel to the Van store is a little too far.  Always a good experience purchasing from Aprils, and will continue to do so albeit   online for my supplies.
response_from_owner_text: Thanks very much Casey, for the most splendid review of our performance. We are delighted you assisted us to find a way to still provide you quality livestock and supplies as closing Burnaby was a sore one however your continued support does not go unnoticed. Thanks for everything cheers Casey.

review_text: I havent been to the store in person but Ive made a couple orders online. The shipping was fast and they were helpful and quick to respond to my email when I had a question. Also they carry Easy Green and Aquarium Co-Op products which is awesome.
response_from_owner_text: Hi,  You are awesome for providing this fantastic review and we are delighted you are happy with our offerings / service and support.  Thanks for everything and of course we hope to hear from you again very soon @yourlocalfishstore

review_text: Visited Aprils Aquarium a few weeks ago to get some supplies (plants, stones, food, and of course shrimp) for my 3rd tank which was also from Aprils - a 15gallon rimless tank which is just perfect. Darrin and Jacob were very helpful and friendly as always...so thank you again! Everything is in place at home now, and my little daughter is so excited to see all the colorful shrimp swimming around and thriving! Also, really glad that they are carrying a nice variety of Aquarium Co-op products now - and love the expanded selection of livestock.
response_from_owner_text: Hi Jason, thank-you so much for making the time and consideration to provide us a fantastic review. We are delighted you and your family are enjoying and flourishing in our great hobby together and without doubt we appreciate all your support. Please come and visit us again very soon @yourlocalfishstore.

review_text: Absolutely the best store for nano fish and planted tanks I have ever seen in my 25+ years in the hobby. An unbelievable assortment of exotic fish, amazing variety of hard scape supplies, and great service. So happy I found this store!
response_from_owner_text: Pam - wow , this review blew me over. What a fantastic testimony to our small business, we love love love it, thank-you so much.  We are SO happy you found us and so happy we tick all the boxes for you this is our goal and we are always striving to improve products , service and support so to learn we are on the right path is so awesome. Your the best and of course we hope to see you again very soon @yourlocalfishstore.  cheers

review_text: By far one of my top choices for aquarium products and supplies! I have been happily shopping at Aprils Aquarium for well over two years and will continue to do so given the great experience everytime. The store carries a wide array of sought after aquarium brands and products in addition to offering a generous selection of popular and unique freshwater fish species that cater to both the beginner and seasoned aquarists. Additionally, the store quarrantines shipments of livestock, quite rare today, thereby going the extra mile for ensuring the health of customers own aquariums. On top of their exceptional product, Darrin and his exceptional team always provide positive service by truly putting the customers needs first! In a recent interaction at Aprils Aquarium, Darrin compassionately helped accommodate my specific needs to help setup an aquarium and thoughtfully provided item suggestions rather than being pushy. Truly shows the teams patience and compassion to supporting the aquarium industry!
response_from_owner_text: Jordan , thank-you so much for this outstanding and well thought out review it certainly hits the spot. Our offering is expanding all the time and we are always looking for more positive synergies to compliant our current structure and with that comes more interest and enthusiasm from you the customer in our great hobby which is obviously a win- win, thus we are delighted  with your very positive and reinforcing comments. Thanks again for all your support and patronage and of course I am sure we will see you again soon @yourlocalfishstore

review_text: Absolute hidden gem! Such a fantastic place to go if you are thinking of starting, or wanting to continue, your fish journey. Darrin, and his staff, are incredibly kind and chalk full of good advice when it comes to designing your dream tank! Won t be going anywhere else again. I went in with my girlfriend who needed some plants for her own planted tank, and basically walked out with an entire set up for myself! My betta thanks you, Darrin.
response_from_owner_text: Issac , wow what an outstanding detailed review - thank you so much . We do try our level best and it s great to hear we are meeting our objectives. Always happy to see you both and hope to see you again soon or visit us online @yourlocalfishstore

review_text: I finally found someone who I can take advice from with my planted tanks!! I will never buy fertilizers or plants from somewhere else other then Darrin!! Outstanding professional service! Ships fast! Quality plants! Huge plants! Healthy looking! And the list goes on and on! Keep it up Darrin!!!
response_from_owner_text: Thanks very much Matt for the very kind comments. We do try our level best . Thanks for all your support and of course we hope to hear from you again very soon @yourlocalfishstore

review_text: Best fish store in the lower mainland! I used to shop at the Burnaby location and they were great! I visited this Vancouver location a couple of weeks ago (after the two locations merged) and was blown away! The store is huge and clean and has an excellent selection of fish and supplies. I love that they carry all of the Aquarium Co-Op products -- lots of stock, too! They also have a big parking lot and parking wasnt an issue during busy hours on the weekend. The staff are all super friendly and helpful. I also spent a long time chatting with the owner to troubleshoot issues Im having with my tank. He went above and beyond to help and the suggestions he and the staff gave are working! The fish are always super healthy from here, too! I will definitely continue to be a regular--worth the extra drive even if you dont live nearby.
response_from_owner_text: Lauren , wow what a fantastic detailed review we love it . Can t thank you and all our clients for amazing support. This review ticks all the boxes and we do really appreciate it . Thanks for your continued support and of course we hope to see you again very soon @ yourlocalfishstore cheers

review_text: First time ordering livestock from Aprils . They shipped packages as promised. They arrived in excellent condition. Great detail to packages. Any questions I had were answered in a timely manner.
response_from_owner_text: Jack,  thank-you for your very valuable business and your most excellent review. We hope to hear from you again very soon @yourlocalfishstore

review_text: This Aquarium store is really the only one I go to, Ive got nothing but positive things to say about the staff who works there and the variety of generally everything they have! Everyone there works so hard to keep everything in order and most importantly prioritizes customer needs with warm smiles on their faces. For instance, Jacob would eagerly go out of his way and search through the whole tank to pick out the best apistogrammas for me because I wanted the best parents for my breeding project. Everyone there gives a friendly and welcoming atmosphere, you have to pay them a visit!!
response_from_owner_text: Hi Harry,  what a great and detailed review we cannot thank-you enough for all the very positive comments. We appareicvate all your support and dedication to the hobby and of course your valuable business. Hope to see you again very soon @yourlocalfishstore cheers  to you Harry.

review_text: :O absolutely stunning store! Fantastic prices, super healthy and unique fish, so many great employees that all know their stuff!!! Just picked up a giant box full of driftwood for a bargain! I could spend hours in this store!
response_from_owner_text: Brian, this is an absolute belter ( as they say in Scotland) just what the doctor ordered and we are delighted your happy with our overall package. Hope to see you again very soon sir @ yourlocalfishstore and thanks again for all your support.

review_text: I go to this place for all my fish hobby needs since they opened here. They treat me like a friend and family. Any question I had they were answering patiently. I like just walk around and look at the set ups in the tanks at front. So much so that I wanted to set up a cube tank. Today when I told they they gave me one free evendough I didnt have enough points yet. Today I mentioned that my drift wood too long and I wasnt able to cut it, rightaway they told me to bring it in and they will cut it for me. Thank you. Just made my week. Lol Thank you so much for making me so happy. This is a great way to keep your costumers happy and keep coming back Now a couple of years went buy. My opinion  didnt change. They are still very nice to every one  treating you like family. The store is better now. Display tanks are amazing. So much so that I copied their style. The fish supply is endless. Plenty of plants to make your tanks georgous. I think I can say this place is the best in town for all you needs.
response_from_owner_text: Klara , thanks very much for the great review we appreciate it very much and we hope to see you again very soon.

review_text: Ordered online Aug 6.Darrin emailed to let me know the next day was a stat holiday, and would ship Tuesday, which was happened. Recd in 2 days, Vancouver, BC to Kitchener, ON. Everything as ordered. Competitive prices,  #1 super service, and great that they have Aquarium Co-op products.
response_from_owner_text: Frank - what a review sir - exactly what we strive for and we really appreciate your feedback and of course your valuable support.  Delighted to be of service and support sir and of course we hope to hear from you again very soon @yourlocalfishstore cheers Frank

review_text: Excellent product line with good stock. Shipping is fast and well packaged. The customer service is nothing short of outstanding!
response_from_owner_text: Barry   Outstanding  we will take that sir ! All day long ! Thank-you for your continued support and of course we hope to hear from you again very soon @yourlocalfishstore

review_text: I placed my first order with April s Aquarium. I must say the process was seamless. Access in Canada to Aquarium Co-Op products is fantastic. -Easy order and payment processing. - delivered well before expected date. - personalized email from the owner checking if I was satisfied with products and service. Don t hesitate to order from this company. They have service nailed down tight. Looking forward to my next order.
